dataset_id: BOREAS Follow-On DSP-01 Landsat TM Land Cover Mosaic of the BOREAS Transect
title: BOREAS Follow-On DSP-01 Landsat TM Land Cover Mosaic of the BOREAS Transect
summary: The objective of this land cover mosaic is to provide a data product that characterizes the detailed land cover of a significant portion of the BOREAS Region. Seven Landsat-5 TM images have been assembled to completely cover the BOREAS Transect.
